transcript_llm: Hey there! I totally get what you mean about sunny days lifting your spirits—I mean, who doesn't love a good dose of Vitamin D, right? But on the flip side, if it's gloomy for too long, it can definitely start to dampen my mood. How about you? Do you find rainy days calming or a bit of a downer?
